io.temporal.common.interceptors

Interface WorkflowOutboundCallsInterceptor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    WorkflowOutboundCallsInterceptorBase

    public interface WorkflowOutboundCallsInterceptor
    Can be used to intercept workflow code calls to the Temporal APIs. An instance should be created through WorkflowInterceptor.interceptWorkflow(WorkflowInboundCallsInterceptor). An interceptor instance must forward all the calls to the next interceptor passed to the interceptExecuteWorkflow call.

    The calls to the interceptor are executed in the context of a workflow and must follow the same rules all the other workflow code follows.
